        "**Interaction** - Lines of code working together to manipulate the same data.\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "```\n",
        "int x = 5;  // if x changes to my_var\n",
        "cout << x;  // must change x here too\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "hWPmvs_Z-Ls_"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "**Possible interactions with n lines of code:** n(n-1)/2 = (n²-n)/2\n",
        "\n",
        "**Ex** : 10 lines = 45 interactions"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "gdvbC6uv-7ph"
      }
