      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "**Problems with large software:**\n",
        "1. Greater likelihood of error\n",
        "2. More diffucult to debug & modify\n",
        "\n",
        "**Control software interaction:**\n",
        "1. Write small units of code\n",
        "2. Minimize interactions/coupling\n",
        "3. Enforce strict rules on how code interacts\n",
        "\n",
        "**Done using:**\n",
        "1. Principles of Software Engineering\n",
        "2. Object Oriented Programming\n",
